{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_27","type":"reasoning","text":"**Inspecting key handling issues**\n\nI need to look into the home screen's key handling, particularly for A. It seems that item selection might not be triggering because a child component isn't emitting key events. I’m thinking about checking the FocusScope and the key mapping in ui/home.slint, especially the potential mismatch between Key.Return and Key.Enter. The controller might be sending KEY_ENTER as a Return string while event.text refers to Key.Return. I'll need to check the key handler in home.slint for confirmation."}}
